abc-123
database_password: 123456
password_key: 123456

➜   ansible-vault view example.yaml
Vault password:
abc-123456
database_password: 123456
password_key: 123456

➜   ansible-vault view example.yaml --vault-password-file=vault_pass.txt
abc-123456
database_password: 123456
password_key: 123456

➜   ansible localhost -m debug -a var="password_key" -e @example.yaml
